---
title: Whipped Peanut Butter & Fruit Snack Board with Cheddar, Ants on a Log, Nut Mix, Fig Jam & Honey
description: If you’ve ever been caught with your spoon in the peanut butter jar, we’re here for you! Here’s how we handle our own “peanut butter problem”: we whip it with crème fraîche and a pinch of salt, shmear it on celery and dot with raisins, plus layer it onto a platter surrounded with other yummy tidbits! Tangy cheddar cheese, sliced apple, pistachio-walnut trail mix, fig jam, honey, and toasted baguette slices make a salty-sweet choose-your-own-adventure meal that’s as tasty as it is beautiful to behold.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65e744be3251bf1977c06017-bebf0964.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65e744be3251bf1977c06017.pdf
